data.title: Felin
data.description: Original cup holder lanyard, with cotton strap and matching cup holder, 100% adaptable and made in resistant silicone. The perfect accessory for festival lovers, to enjoy events with no ties.

data.title: Bosgo
data.description: Nature line wristband made in resistant 100% cotton, with unidirectional safety closure made in bamboo.

data.title: Fonten
data.description: Unbreakable synthetic fibre bracelet for events. With safety adhesive closure, water resistant and presented in a die-cut plate of 10 pieces individually numbered. One size fits all for adults and available in a wide range of colours.

data.title: Zerolox
data.description: Rainbow flag with multicoloured fabric in resistant polyester and fastening straps. A flag to be proud of.

data.title: Genax
data.description: Fun animation wig in bright tones with curly hair. Also available in Spanish design.

data.title: Martyns
data.description: Original eyeglass frame without lenses with frames in a wide range of bright tones. Presented in a padded polyester cover with self-closing laces.

data.title: Rolof
data.description: Polyester flag. With 30 cm pole and 20 x 13,5 cm flag. Available in a wide range of colours.

data.title: Lessep

data.title: Drentox

data.title: Heldex
data.description: Flag in resistant polyester of vivid colors with a reinforced graphic surface of 55x115cm. Compatible with item 5422: Backpack with Flag Carrier Heldex.

data.description: Fun animation hand in EVA material. With a wide printing area and illustrations at both sides of the item. Available in a wide range of colors.

data.title: Portel
data.description: Polyester pennant flag in XL size -80x30 cm fabric- in a wide range of vivid colors. Flagpole in white color.

data.title: Dambor
data.description: XL size flag -100x70 cm- in soft polyester and in a wide range of vivid colors. Including resistant, matching color straps.

data.title: Dolim
data.description: Digital hand tally counter, manufactured in durable ABS material with glossy finish. Practical polyester lanyard and wide counter buttons to add or deduct capacity. Digital LCD screen with 4 digit counter and reset button on top. Wide logo area, especially designed for pad printing. Presented in an attractive design box. Battery powered, button cell included.

data.title: Yoksy
data.description: Hand tally counter, manufactured in durable ABS material with glossy finish. Practical finger holder in metal, with comfy push button and 4 digit counter, including reset button on one side. Wide logo area, especially designed for pad printing. Presented in an attractive design box.

data.title: Multi
data.description: PVC bracelet in a wide range of bright tones. With adjustable hook and loop safety lock.

data.title: Rostel
data.description: Cushion made in durable non-woven, with thick padding, carrying handle and pocket for branding. Available in a wide range of colours.

data.title: Forlong
data.description: Whistle with distinctive design and made of durable PS. With matching color neck string and available in a wide range of colours.

data.title: Sowel
data.description: Event wristband with a nature finish. Made of Tyvekï¿½ synthetic fibre, especially remarkable for its resistance, durability and easy printability. Waterproof and with adhesive closure, one size fits all for adults. Presented in a 10-piece die-cut sheet with individual numbering.

data.title: Broch
data.description: Nature line, event wristband. In RPET polyester 160g/m2, made from recycled plastic to promote the reuse of plastic waste and contribute to the sustainability of the planet. With bamboo fastener and available in a wide range of colours, white colour specially designed for sublimation printing. RPET emblem printed on the wristband.

data.title: Bayala
data.description: Nature line, event wristband. Made in 100% cork, to promote the use of natural materials and contribute to the sustainability of the planet. Water resistant, adjustable and with safety closure.

data.title: Floid
data.description: Eyeglass frame without lenses in an original bicolor design in a varied tones.

data.title: Solidario
data.description: Ribbon pin with glossy body finish in varied colors and matching color ribbon.
